The budget is deemed safe-that is, safe against another such a lengthy debate as occurred on Sir E. B. LYTTON'S amendment, but not against various side-wind attacks on different portions of the plan.

headline.main: RURAL ECONOMY.; Gleanings of Fact and Practice in Fruit Culture. Noxious Insects.

docs.lead_paragraph: APHIS OR PLANT LOUSE, aphis, plant louse, puccron, or vine fretter, is a genus of insects comprising many species and varieties, which are so denominated from the plants they infest. They are got rid of sometimes, when on trees, by syringing with water, or elder leaves infused in water, or common soap suds; sulphur has also been found to promote the health of plants on which it has been sprinkled, especially Deach trees.

Whorter, who for eight years, has held the position of ticket-seller at Buffalo, to the Rochester and Buffalo Railway Company, and who is now compelled to resign his situation on account of declining health, having lost his eye-sight, has been presented by the Directors of the Company with the sum of $2,000.

docs.lead_paragraph: It becomes our painful task, says the Augusta Constitutionalist, of the 19th inst., to announce the death of Major GEORGE L. TWIGGS, a well known, prominent and respected citizen of this community. After lingering and painful illness of thirteen weeks, he died on Monday, at his Summer residence, nine miles below the city, in the 64th year of his age.

headline.main: CITY.; Trial for Murder on the High Seas.

docs.lead_paragraph: U. S. CIRCUIT COURT.--Before Chief Justice NELSON.--The Homicide on board the ship American congress.--MICHAEL REARDEN was put to the bar on an indictment charging him with the murder of HENRY MILLER, while on board the ship American congress, on the 12th of April last, by striking him on the head with a belaying pin.

headline.main: ONE DAY LATER FROM ASPINWALL.; Arrival of the Crescent City and Uncle Sam,. Health of the Isthmus, &c.

docs.lead_paragraph: Both the Uncle Sam and Crescent City arrived from Aspinwall yesterday morning. Their California dates are no later than those by the Union. The Isthmus news by the Uncle Sam is one day later. We are indebted to Pursers BUCKMAN and BULLAY for early deliveries.
